(106, '2015-08-12 10:10:00', NULL, 1, 26, 'Jupiter Ascending', 'jupiter_ascending', 1, 'Jupiter Jones was born under a night sky&#44; with signs predicting that she was destined for great things. Now grown&#44; Jupiter dreams of the stars but wakes up to the cold reality of a job cleaning other people&#39;s houses and an endless run of bad breaks. Only when Caine Wise&#44; a genetically engineered ex-military hunter&#44; arrives on Earth to track her down does Jupiter begin to glimpse the fate that has been waiting for her all along - her genetic signature marks her as next in line for an extraordinary inheritance that could alter the balance of the cosmos.                ', '<p>Jupiter Jones was born under a night sky&#44; with signs predicting that she was destined for great things. Now grown&#44; Jupiter dreams of the stars but wakes up to the cold reality of a job cleaning other people&#39;s houses and an endless run of bad breaks. Only when Caine Wise&#44; a genetically engineered ex-military hunter&#44; arrives on Earth to track her down does Jupiter begin to glimpse the fate that has been waiting for her all along - her genetic signature marks her as next in line for an extraordinary inheritance that could alter the balance of the cosmos.                </p>\n', '29487770f42a26d4a8a4853fc662d111', 1, 1439367000, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '1617661', '76757', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/aMEsvTUklw0uZ3gk3Q6lAj6302a.jpg', 'Action&#44; Adventure&#44; Sci-Fi', 'Andy Wachowski', 'ChanningTatum&#44;MilaKunis&#44;EddieRedmayne', 'USA&#44; UK&#44; Australia', 'English', '2015-02-27', '02:07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/4liSXBZZdURI0c1Id1zLJo6Z3Gu.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi2504305177/', 'acf9d83e1c295c8'),
