(108, '2015-08-12 10:10:00', NULL, 1, 28, 'John Wick', 'john_wick', 1, 'John Wick is a mob hit man who&#44; upon falling in love&#44; quits. 5 years later&#44; his wife dies and to make sure he&#39;s not alone she arranges for a dog to be brought to him after her death. Later&#44; some men wanting his car break in and beat him up and kill his dog. When he recovers&#44; he sets to get the ones who killed his dog. He learns that the leader is the son of his former employer. And the man wanting to protect his son&#44; tries to take care of Wick but he&#39;s still as good as he was.                ', '<p>John Wick is a mob hit man who&#44; upon falling in love&#44; quits. 5 years later&#44; his wife dies and to make sure he&#39;s not alone she arranges for a dog to be brought to him after her death. Later&#44; some men wanting his car break in and beat him up and kill his dog. When he recovers&#44; he sets to get the ones who killed his dog. He learns that the leader is the son of his former employer. And the man wanting to protect his son&#44; tries to take care of Wick but he&#39;s still as good as he was.                </p>\n', '40eaedfc1a5dd92925f5786e5981a929', 1, 1439367000, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '2911666', '245891', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/sq2MmFv9sanl9PFMfbdaBLveSJ8.jpg', 'Action&#44; Thriller', 'Chad Stahelski', 'KeanuReeves&#44;MichaelNyqvist&#44;AlfieAllen', 'USA', 'English', '2014-10-24', '00:00', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mFb0ygcue4ITixDkdr7wm1Tdarx.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi884911897/', 'd11a7bb75222a44'),
