(130, '2015-08-12 10:10:00', NULL, 1, 50, 'Salt', 'salt', 1, 'Evelyn Salt is a CIA agent and highly respected by all&#44; including her boss&#44; Ted Winter. Out of the blue&#44; a Russian spy walks into their offices and offers a vital piece of information: the President of Russia will be assassinated during his forthcoming visit to New York City to attend the funeral of the recently deceased U.S. Vice President. The name of the assassin: Evelyn Salt. Concerned about the safety of her husband&#44; who she cannot contact&#44; she goes on the run. Winter refuses to accept that she is a mole or a double agent but her actions begin to raise doubts. Just who is Evelyn Salt and what is she planning&#63;                ', '<p>Evelyn Salt is a CIA agent and highly respected by all&#44; including her boss&#44; Ted Winter. Out of the blue&#44; a Russian spy walks into their offices and offers a vital piece of information: the President of Russia will be assassinated during his forthcoming visit to New York City to attend the funeral of the recently deceased U.S. Vice President. The name of the assassin: Evelyn Salt. Concerned about the safety of her husband&#44; who she cannot contact&#44; she goes on the run. Winter refuses to accept that she is a mole or a double agent but her actions begin to raise doubts. Just who is Evelyn Salt and what is she planning&#63;                </p>\n', '226c50d032597970b70c1a5cf8d12edb', 1, 1439367000, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0944835', '27576', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/956xMjH4sPoqimqoLOP6AI19mjm.jpg', 'Action&#44; Crime&#44; Mystery&#44; Thriller', 'Phillip Noyce', 'AngelinaJolie&#44;LievSchreiber&#44;ChiwetelEjiofor', 'USA', 'English', '2010-07-23', '01:40', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vHLsgsvLtFWDlhBigKDRsYIC1p6.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi1217987865/', '64e123ea511bbfd'),
(131, '2015-08-12 10:10:00', NULL, 1, 51, 'Da bing xiao jiang', 'da_bing_xiao_jiang', 1, 'Two armies clash in ancient war-torn China; none survive but a young general from a royal house and a farmer foot soldier who binds the fallen leader to take him home and claim a reward. Many stand in their way: an abandoned songstress&#44; the noble&#39;s own murderous younger brother&#44; desperate beggars&#44; rough slavers&#44; and the pair&#39;s own differing agendas. Through it all&#44; a bond forms between the two&#44; and what will happen at journey&#39;s end becomes anyone&#39;s guess.                ', '<p>Two armies clash in ancient war-torn China; none survive but a young general from a royal house and a farmer foot soldier who binds the fallen leader to take him home and claim a reward. Many stand in their way: an abandoned songstress&#44; the noble&#39;s own murderous younger brother&#44; desperate beggars&#44; rough slavers&#44; and the pair&#39;s own differing agendas. Through it all&#44; a bond forms between the two&#44; and what will happen at journey&#39;s end becomes anyone&#39;s guess.                </p>\n', '766b4bdd9f2700d8b1fe2562c740edbe', 1, 1439367000, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '1319718', '35138', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/am1R6cNx98qvJloH7ufiwWLsyfu.jpg', 'Action&#44; Adventure&#44; Comedy', 'Sheng Ding', 'JackieChan&#44;LeehomWang&#44;Sung-junYoo', 'China&#44; Hong Kong', 'Mandarin', '2010-02-14', '01:36', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/qrVZxIfhIOLUuL8ICGK0V5y6fGD.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi3940719641/', 'c6a608b898374f7'),
