(181, '2015-08-12 10:31:00', NULL, 1, 101, 'The Lone Ranger', 'the_lone_ranger', 1, 'In the 1930s&#44; an elderly Tonto tells a young boy the tale of John Reid&#44; the Lone Ranger. An idealistic lawyer&#44; he rides with his brother and fellow Texas Rangers in pursuit of the notorious Butch Cavendish. Ambushed by the outlaw and left for dead&#44; John Reid is rescued by the renegade Comanche&#44; Tonto&#44; at the insistence of a mysterious white horse and offers to help him to bring Cavendish to justice. Becoming a reluctant masked rider with a seemingly incomprehensible partner&#44; Reid pursues the criminal against all obstacles. However&#44; John and Tonto learn that Cavendish is only part of a far greater injustice and the pair must fight it in an adventure that would make them a legend.                ', '<p>In the 1930s&#44; an elderly Tonto tells a young boy the tale of John Reid&#44; the Lone Ranger. An idealistic lawyer&#44; he rides with his brother and fellow Texas Rangers in pursuit of the notorious Butch Cavendish. Ambushed by the outlaw and left for dead&#44; John Reid is rescued by the renegade Comanche&#44; Tonto&#44; at the insistence of a mysterious white horse and offers to help him to bring Cavendish to justice. Becoming a reluctant masked rider with a seemingly incomprehensible partner&#44; Reid pursues the criminal against all obstacles. However&#44; John and Tonto learn that Cavendish is only part of a far greater injustice and the pair must fight it in an adventure that would make them a legend.                </p>\n', '94844dcc6e4bafa11de97c3fc42d53ea', 1, 1439368260, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '1210819', '57201', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/b4vil5ueYJNBNypHmo1tpuevh4z.jpg', 'Action&#44; Adventure&#44; Western', 'Gore Verbinski', 'JohnnyDepp&#44;ArmieHammer&#44;WilliamFichtner', 'USA', 'English', '2013-07-03', '02:29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/sgcgfrlOOB6lVXbfl75YTszF4jI.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/