(242, '2015-08-12 11:06:00', NULL, 1, 162, 'Cars 2', 'cars_2', 1, 'After Mater gets his best friend&#44; star race car Lightning McQueen&#44; a spot in the very first World Grand Prix&#44; he is given the job of pit crew chief. But while they are in Japan&#44; Mater crosses paths with Holly Shiftwell&#44; a spy searching for an American spy. Unknown to Mater&#44; the American spy attached a tracking device on him while being attacked. Thinking the tow truck is the spy&#44; Holly and another spy&#44; Finn McMissile&#44; take Mater around the world to find and stop an evil plot created by &quot;lemons&#44;&quot; old cars considered ugly.                ', '<p>After Mater gets his best friend&#44; star race car Lightning McQueen&#44; a spot in the very first World Grand Prix&#44; he is given the job of pit crew chief. But while they are in Japan&#44; Mater crosses paths with Holly Shiftwell&#44; a spy searching for an American spy. Unknown to Mater&#44; the American spy attached a tracking device on him while being attacked. Thinking the tow truck is the spy&#44; Holly and another spy&#44; Finn McMissile&#44; take Mater around the world to find and stop an evil plot created by &quot;lemons&#44;&quot; old cars considered ugly.                </p>\n', 'df196a66a54814880388ac3b0f6bc2cc', 1, 1439370360, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '1216475', '49013', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7WILDjnJggB3bIioS3LRvtvmu1X.jpg', 'Animation&#44; Adventure&#44; Comedy&#44; Family&#44; Sport', 'John Lasseter', 'OwenWilson&#44;LarrytheCableGuy&#44;MichaelCaine', 'USA', 'English', '2011-06-16', '00:00', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jEcmZhtJkZQc6ta2vzBd9CU7GIx.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi1822465049/', NULL),
