(244, '2015-08-12 11:07:00', NULL, 1, 164, 'Up', 'up', 1, 'A young Carl Fredrickson meets a young adventure-spirited girl named Ellie. They both dream of going to a lost land in South America. 70 years later&#44; Ellie has died. Carl remembers the promise he made to her. Then&#44; when he inadvertently hits a construction worker&#44; he is forced to go to a retirement home. But before they can take him&#44; he and his house fly away. However&#44; he has a stowaway aboard: an 8-year-old boy named Russell&#44; who&#39;s trying to get an Assisting the Elderly badge. Together&#44; they embark on an adventure&#44; where they encounter talking dogs&#44; an evil villain and a rare bird named Kevin.                ', '<p>A young Carl Fredrickson meets a young adventure-spirited girl named Ellie. They both dream of going to a lost land in South America. 70 years later&#44; Ellie has died. Carl remembers the promise he made to her. Then&#44; when he inadvertently hits a construction worker&#44; he is forced to go to a retirement home. But before they can take him&#44; he and his house fly away. However&#44; he has a stowaway aboard: an 8-year-old boy named Russell&#44; who&#39;s trying to get an Assisting the Elderly badge. Together&#44; they embark on an adventure&#44; where they encounter talking dogs&#44; an evil villain and a rare bird named Kevin.                </p>\n', '007d279a59c599e413443ccd364e310b', 1, 1439370420, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '1049413', '14160', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gfFqBcoFW8uczyl2ytVmVmUg82k.jpg', 'Animation&#44; Adventure&#44; Comedy&#44; Family', 'Pete Docter', 'EdwardAsner&#44;JordanNagai&#44;JohnRatzenberger', 'USA', 'English', '2009-05-13', '01:36', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fI3ucpgaVKOUcQ82vhgWmWuLlg2.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi2557280793/', 'f55153ba719ce35');
