(265, '2015-08-12 11:32:00', NULL, 1, 185, 'Kaze tachinu', 'kaze_tachinu', 1, 'Jiro dreams of flying and designing beautiful airplanes&#44; inspired by the famous Italian aeronautical designer Caproni. Nearsighted from a young age and unable to be a pilot&#44; Jiro joins a major Japanese engineering company in 1927 and becomes one of the world&#39;s most innovative and accomplished airplane designers. The film chronicles much of his life&#44; depicting key historical events&#44; including the Great Kanto Earthquake of 1923&#44; the Great Depression&#44; the tuberculosis epidemic and Japan&#39;s plunge into war. Jiro meets and falls in love with Nahoko&#44; and grows and cherishes his friendship with his colleague Honjo.                ', '<p>Jiro dreams of flying and designing beautiful airplanes&#44; inspired by the famous Italian aeronautical designer Caproni. Nearsighted from a young age and unable to be a pilot&#44; Jiro joins a major Japanese engineering company in 1927 and becomes one of the world&#39;s most innovative and accomplished airplane designers. The film chronicles much of his life&#44; depicting key historical events&#44; including the Great Kanto Earthquake of 1923&#44; the Great Depression&#44; the tuberculosis epidemic and Japan&#39;s plunge into war. Jiro meets and falls in love with Nahoko&#44; and grows and cherishes his friendship with his colleague Honjo.                </p>\n', '75200d2252d7741d179a668fb62736cb', 1, 1439371920, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '2013293', '149870', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3OTcCyf7QbGdVxsS8GLtaSsTZtP.jpg', 'Animation&#44; Biography&#44; Drama&#44; Romance&#44; War', 'Hayao Miyazaki', 'HideakiAnno&#44;HidetoshiNishijima&#44;MioriTakimoto', 'Japan', 'Japanese', '2013-07-20', '02:06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/cMrvn4Hl0A0NAL61BpDWQIsMsiN.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi155101209/', '1764270286c9566'),
(266, '2015-08-12 11:32:00', NULL, 1, 186, 'The Runaways', 'the_runaways', 1, 'In 1975&#44; San Fernando Valley teen Joan Larkin reinvents herself as Joan Jett&#44; a guitarist who wants to form an all-girl punk band. She pitches the idea to a sleazy manager&#44; Kim Fowley&#44; who pairs her with a drummer and then searches for a face: he finds Cherie Currie&#44; at age 15&#44; the perfect jailbait image for his purpose; by luck&#44; she can sing. Two others round out the band&#44; The Runaways. Fowley books a tour&#44; signs them to Mercury Records&#44; and packs them off to crowds in Japan. Seeds of conflict sprout early: Fowley puts Cherie front and center in the publicity&#44; she&#39;s soon strung out on drugs and vodka&#44; and jealousies arise. Without adult supervision&#44; where can Joan and Cherie end up&#63;                ', '<p>In 1975&#44; San Fernando Valley teen Joan Larkin reinvents herself as Joan Jett&#44; a guitarist who wants to form an all-girl punk band. She pitches the idea to a sleazy manager&#44; Kim Fowley&#44; who pairs her with a drummer and then searches for a face: he finds Cherie Currie&#44; at age 15&#44; the perfect jailbait image for his purpose; by luck&#44; she can sing. Two others round out the band&#44; The Runaways. Fowley books a tour&#44; signs them to Mercury Records&#44; and packs them off to crowds in Japan. Seeds of conflict sprout early: Fowley puts Cherie front and center in the publicity&#44; she&#39;s soon strung out on drugs and vodka&#44; and jealousies arise. Without adult supervision&#44; where can Joan and Cherie end up&#63;                </p>\n', '8eecc99483cbbef78bb69ec74075d9f7', 1, 1439371920, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '1017451', '27586', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rC8PTdRj1Ij4Baz3jWCCgCV6JeX.jpg', 'Biography&#44; Drama&#44; History&#44; Music', 'Floria Sigismondi', 'KristenStewart&#44;DakotaFanning&#44;MichaelShannon', 'USA', 'English', '2010-03-19', '01:46', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t