(271, '2015-08-12 11:32:00', NULL, 1, 191, 'The World&#39;s Fastest Indian', 'the_world&#39;s_fastest_indian', 1, 'For 25 years in Invercargill at the south end of New Zealand&#44; Burt Munro (1899-1978) has been working on increasing the speed of his motorcycle&#44; a 1920 Indian. He dreams of taking it to the Bonneville Salt Flats to see how fast it will go. By the early 1960s&#44; heart disease threatens his life&#44; so he mortgages his house and takes a boat to Los Angeles&#44; buys an old car&#44; builds a makeshift trailer&#44; gets the Indian through customs&#44; and heads for Utah. Along the way&#44; people he meets are charmed by his open&#44; direct friendliness. If he makes it to Bonneville&#44; will they let an old guy on the flats with makeshift tires&#44; no brakes&#44; and no chute&#63; And will the Indian actually respond&#63;                ', '<p>For 25 years in Invercargill at the south end of New Zealand&#44; Burt Munro (1899-1978) has been working on increasing the speed of his motorcycle&#44; a 1920 Indian. He dreams of taking it to the Bonneville Salt Flats to see how fast it will go. By the early 1960s&#44; heart disease threatens his life&#44; so he mortgages his house and takes a boat to Los Angeles&#44; buys an old car&#44; builds a makeshift trailer&#44; gets the Indian through customs&#44; and heads for Utah. Along the way&#44; people he meets are charmed by his open&#44; direct friendliness. If he makes it to Bonneville&#44; will they let an old guy on the flats with makeshift tires&#44; no brakes&#44; and no chute&#63; And will the Indian actually respond&#63;                </p>\n', '0c940ee455e448e5548063bf859ecd91', 1, 1439371920, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0412080', '9912', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/h3xDXEEjppiyuRtMv6Cy5bcMTrG.jpg', 'Biography&#44; Drama&#44; Sport', 'Roger Donaldson', 'AnthonyHopkins&#44;DianeLadd&#44;IainRea', 'New Zealand&#44; USA&#44; Switzerland&#44; Japan', 'English', '2005-10-13', '02: