(274, '2015-08-12 11:33:00', NULL, 1, 194, 'Casino', 'casino', 1, 'This Martin Scorsese film depicts the Janus-like quality of Las Vegas--it has a glittering&#44; glamorous face&#44; as well as a brutal&#44; cruel one. Ace Rothstein and Nicky Santoro&#44; mobsters who move to Las Vegas to make their mark&#44; live and work in this paradoxical world. Seen through their eyes&#44; each as a foil to the other&#44; the details of mob involvement in the casinos of the 1970&#39;s and &#39;80&#39;s are revealed. Ace is the smooth operator of the Tangiers casino&#44; while Nicky is his boyhood friend and tough strongman&#44; robbing and shaking down the locals. However&#44; they each have a tragic flaw--Ace falls in love with a hustler&#44; Ginger&#44; and Nicky falls into an ever-deepening spiral of drugs and violence.                ', '<p>This Martin Scorsese film depicts the Janus-like quality of Las Vegas--it has a glittering&#44; glamorous face&#44; as well as a brutal&#44; cruel one. Ace Rothstein and Nicky Santoro&#44; mobsters who move to Las Vegas to make their mark&#44; live and work in this paradoxical world. Seen through their eyes&#44; each as a foil to the other&#44; the details of mob involvement in the casinos of the 1970&#39;s and &#39;80&#39;s are revealed. Ace is the smooth operator of the Tangiers casino&#44; while Nicky is his boyhood friend and tough strongman&#44; robbing and shaking down the locals. However&#44; they each have a tragic flaw--Ace falls in love with a hustler&#44; Ginger&#44; and Nicky falls into an ever-deepening spiral of drugs and violence.                </p>\n', '3f662da50ce516b12dac255075bfd2c7', 1, 1439371980, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0112641', '524', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xo517ibXBDdYQY81j0WIG7BVcWq.jpg', 'Biography&#44; Crime&#44; Drama', 'Martin Scorsese', 'RobertDeNiro&#44;SharonStone&#44;JoePesci', 'USA&#44; France', 'English', '1995-11-22', '02:58', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3ofB3pVFY