(338, '2015-08-12 11:36:00', NULL, 1, 258, 'Music and Lyrics', 'music_and_lyrics', 1, 'Cheery Alex Fletcher lives comfortably in Manhattan off the residuals from his 80&#39;s pop success and reprising his hits at school reunions&#44; theme parks&#44; and state fairs. But those gigs are declining&#44; so he jumps at the chance to write a song and record it with reigning teen idol Cora Corman. Trouble is&#44; he&#39;s good at melodies but needs a lyricist and has less than a week to finish. Enter Sophie Fisher&#44; subbing for a friend who waters Alex&#39;s plants; she&#39;s a pretty good poet&#44; quick witted&#44; and could do it&#44; if she&#39;d agree. But there&#39;s some sort of shadow over her head that Alex may not be able to charm his way past. And what if they do get a song written&#44; what then&#63;                ', '<p>Cheery Alex Fletcher lives comfortably in Manhattan off the residuals from his 80&#39;s pop success and reprising his hits at school reunions&#44; theme parks&#44; and state fairs. But those gigs are declining&#44; so he jumps at the chance to write a song and record it with reigning teen idol Cora Corman. Trouble is&#44; he&#39;s good at melodies but needs a lyricist and has less than a week to finish. Enter Sophie Fisher&#44; subbing for a friend who waters Alex&#39;s plants; she&#39;s a pretty good poet&#44; quick witted&#44; and could do it&#44; if she&#39;d agree. But there&#39;s some sort of shadow over her head that Alex may not be able to charm his way past. And what if they do get a song written&#44; what then&#63;                </p>\n', '952de5f1c7a1408cf20a4227c7c989ff', 1, 1439372160, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0758766', '11172', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jhv9qSAuwGkzVj1pSnu3HQBb8Qe.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Music&#44; Romance', 'Marc Lawrence', 'HughGrant&#44;DrewBarrymore&#44;ScottPorter', 'USA', 'English', '2007-02-09', '01:35', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/t6FwromtGll1dOwVwRu8YcWQdZO.jpg', 'http://ww