(339, '2015-08-12 11:36:00', NULL, 1, 259, 'Norbit', 'norbit', 1, 'Norbit is a normal person&#44; who after being adopted by Mr. Wong&#44; ends up being married to the very large&#44; Rasputia. Norbit&#39;s childhood love&#44; Kate Thomas arrives back in town to buy the orphanage. Norbit sees this as his chance to get back together with Kate&#44; until he discovers that she is in fact engaged to Deion Hughes. Norbit isn&#39;t going to lay this to rest&#44; whilst he tries to survive life with Rasputia&#44; and it looks like Deion also has something he would like to keep secret.                ', '<p>Norbit is a normal person&#44; who after being adopted by Mr. Wong&#44; ends up being married to the very large&#44; Rasputia. Norbit&#39;s childhood love&#44; Kate Thomas arrives back in town to buy the orphanage. Norbit sees this as his chance to get back together with Kate&#44; until he discovers that she is in fact engaged to Deion Hughes. Norbit isn&#39;t going to lay this to rest&#44; whilst he tries to survive life with Rasputia&#44; and it looks like Deion also has something he would like to keep secret.                </p>\n', 'd90a238980766b584976f79309ebc3e7', 1, 1439372160, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0477051', '9757', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mbScfMvi5xropJmztEgLGwmeo6N.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Drama&#44; Romance', 'Brian Robbins', 'EddieMurphy&#44;ThandieNewton&#44;TerryCrews', 'USA', 'English', '2007-02-08', '00:00', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3ZlkfPqLJjuJYNvPFSnxfgtxTjW.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi228196633/', '93836b1a730a12b'),
(340, '2015-08-12 11:36:00', NULL, 1, 260, 'The Devil Wears Prada', 'the_devil_wears_prada', 1, 'In New York&#44; the simple and naive just-graduated in journalism Andrea Sachs is hired to work as the second assistant of the powerful and sophisticated Miranda Priestly&#44; the ruthless and merciless executive of the Runway fashion magazine. Andrea dreams to become a journalist and faces the opportunity as a temporary professional challenge. The first assistant Emily advises Andrea about the behavior and preferences of their cruel boss&#44; and the stylist Nigel helps Andrea to dress more adequately for the environment. Andrea changes her attitude and behavior&#44; affecting her private life and the relationship with her boyfriend Nate&#44; her family and friends. In the end&#44; Andrea learns that life is made of choices.                ', '<p>In New York&#44; the simple and naive just-graduated in journalism Andrea Sachs is hired to work as the second assistant of the powerful and sophisticated Miranda Priestly&#44; the ruthless and merciless executive of the Runway fashion magazine. Andrea dreams to become a journalist and faces the opportunity as a temporary professional challenge. The first assistant Emily advises Andrea about the behavior and preferences of their cruel boss&#44; and the stylist Nigel helps Andrea to dress more adequately for the environment. Andrea changes her attitude and behavior&#44; affecting her private life and the relationship with her boyfriend Nate&#44; her family and friends. In the end&#44; Andrea learns that life is made of choices.                </p>\n', '6d04d50bbff510140451346d53a9b01a', 1, 1439372160, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0458352', '350', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8unCRm0LeiO0fM6skWAZy3ZfXR1.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Drama&#44; Romance', 'David Frankel', 'AnneHathaway&#44;MerylStreep&#44;AdrianGrenier', 'USA&#44; France', 'English', '2006-06-30', '01:49', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2veJf7wcs1hvJGC