(342, '2015-08-12 11:36:00', NULL, 1, 262, 'Bones', 'bones', 1, 'Brilliant&#44; but socially inept&#44; forensic anthropologist Dr. Temperence Brennan works at the Jeffersonian Institute in Washington DC. After consulting for him on a FBI case&#44; she is approached by cocky yet charming ex-Army Ranger turned Special Agent&#44; Seeley Booth to help the Bureau solve crimes by identifying human remains that are too far gone for standard FBI forensic investigations. Brennan&#39;s empirical&#44; literal view of the world causes friction with Booths emotive&#44; instinctive attitude creating a volatile relationship. However as their case load increases the symbiotic partnership produces results and with the support of Brennan&#39;s Squint Squad&#44; murderers&#44; past and present should be on the look out.                ', '<p>Brilliant&#44; but socially inept&#44; forensic anthropologist Dr. Temperence Brennan works at the Jeffersonian Institute in Washington DC. After consulting for him on a FBI case&#44; she is approached by cocky yet charming ex-Army Ranger turned Special Agent&#44; Seeley Booth to help the Bureau solve crimes by identifying human remains that are too far gone for standard FBI forensic investigations. Brennan&#39;s empirical&#44; literal view of the world causes friction with Booths emotive&#44; instinctive attitude creating a volatile relationship. However as their case load increases the symbiotic partnership produces results and with the support of Brennan&#39;s Squint Squad&#44; murderers&#44; past and present should be on the look out.                </p>\n', '765975684d14c26e502d3c1c1c57170f', 1, 1439372160, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0460627', '1911', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hYqFKoOZ54FOtL7r2WK6gQIMiQg.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Crime&#44; Drama&#44; Mystery&#44; Romance', 'Hart Hanson', 'EmilyDeschanel&#44;DavidBoreanaz&#44;MichaelaConlin', 'USA', 'English', '2005-09-12', '12:40', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8vv0iel