(373, '2015-08-12 11:36:00', NULL, 1, 293, 'Army of Darkness', 'army_of_darkness', 1, 'In this sequel to the Evil Dead films&#44; a discount-store employee (&quot;Name&#39;s Ash. Housewares.&quot;) is time-warped to a medieval castle beset by monstrous forces. Initially mistaken for an enemy&#44; he is soon revealed as the prophecised savior who can quest for the Necronomicon&#44; a book which can dispel the evil. Unfortunately&#44; he screws up the magic words while collecting the tome&#44; and releases an army of skeletons&#44; led by his own Deadite counterpart. What follows is a thrilling&#44; yet tongue-in-cheek battle between Ash&#39;s 20th Century tactics and the minions of darkness.                ', '<p>In this sequel to the Evil Dead films&#44; a discount-store employee (&quot;Name&#39;s Ash. Housewares.&quot;) is time-warped to a medieval castle beset by monstrous forces. Initially mistaken for an enemy&#44; he is soon revealed as the prophecised savior who can quest for the Necronomicon&#44; a book which can dispel the evil. Unfortunately&#44; he screws up the magic words while collecting the tome&#44; and releases an army of skeletons&#44; led by his own Deadite counterpart. What follows is a thrilling&#44; yet tongue-in-cheek battle between Ash&#39;s 20th Century tactics and the minions of darkness.                </p>\n', '66bf7242873cd9f4af4f1227a00cb890', 1, 1439372160, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0106308', '766', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2eZKDIwLNnySbwqQtAaUz0kYDIL.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Fantasy&#44; Horror', 'Sam Raimi', 'BruceCampbell&#44;EmbethDavidtz&#44;MarcusGilbert', 'USA', 'English', '1992-10-09', '01:21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/j7ctTLHSOrvY6fl63CjBNbmkTWq.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi2629239065/', 'fe2133ec78f8da3'),
(374, '2015-08-12 11:37:00', NULL, 1, 294, 'All Dogs Go to Heaven', 'all_dogs_go_to_heaven', 1, 'When a casino owning dog named Charlie is murdered by his rival Carface&#44; he finds himself in Heaven basically by default since all dogs go to heaven. However&#44; since he wants to get back at his killer&#44; he cons his way back to the living with the warning that doing that damns him to Hell. Once back&#44; he teams with his old partner&#44; Itchy to prep his retaliation. He also stumbles on to an orphan girl who can talk to the animals&#44; thus allowing him to get the inside info on the races to ensure his wins to finance his plans. However&#44; all the while&#44; he is still haunted by nightmares on what&#39;s waiting for him on the other side unless he can prove that he is worthy of Heaven again.                ', '<p>When a casino owning dog named Charlie is murdered by his rival Carface&#44; he finds himself in Heaven basically by default since all dogs go to heaven. However&#44; since he wants to get back at his killer&#44; he cons his way back to the living with the warning that doing that damns him to Hell. Once back&#44; he teams with his old partner&#44; Itchy to prep his retaliation. He also stumbles on to an orphan girl who can talk to the animals&#44; thus allowing him to get the inside info on the races to ensure his wins to finance his plans. However&#44; all the while&#44; he is still haunted by nightmares on what&#39;s waiting for him on the other side unless he can prove that he is worthy of Heaven again.                </p>\n', 'a6ad1c6383ded84c72efc273095f933e', 1, 1439372220, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0096787', '11497', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fb6CRpryYQB5eqjohSnLbjHxJQK.jpg', 'Animation&#44; Comedy&#44; Drama&#44; Family&#44; Fantasy', 'Don Bluth', 'DomDeLuise&#44;BurtReynolds&#44;JudithBarsi', 'Ireland&#44; UK&#44; USA', 'English', '1989-11-17', '01:24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/46rKRjko3K3nxbmsB0lh4Z2WyU