(396, '2015-08-12 11:46:00', NULL, 1, 316, 'Identity Thief', 'identity_thief', 1, 'Sandy Patterson (Jason Bateman) gets a nice call confirming his name and other identifying information. The next thing he knows&#44; a spa in Florida is reminding him of his appointment and his credit cards are maxed out. With his identity stolen&#44; Sandy leaves his wife&#44; kids and job to literally bring the thief to justice in Colorado. Keeping tabs on the other Sandy (Melissa McCarthy) and run-ins with bounty hunters is harder than he was expecting&#44; and ultimately the cross-country trip is going to find both Sandys learning life tips from one another.                ', '<p>Sandy Patterson (Jason Bateman) gets a nice call confirming his name and other identifying information. The next thing he knows&#44; a spa in Florida is reminding him of his appointment and his credit cards are maxed out. With his identity stolen&#44; Sandy leaves his wife&#44; kids and job to literally bring the thief to justice in Colorado. Keeping tabs on the other Sandy (Melissa McCarthy) and run-ins with bounty hunters is harder than he was expecting&#44; and ultimately the cross-country trip is going to find both Sandys learning life tips from one another.                </p>\n', 'ca92e174180177557f9b1b2d04805d7f', 1, 1439372760, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '2024432', '109431', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/lOF4rI6SxgRsVLW8odsauqnhB9Z.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Crime', 'Seth Gordon', 'JasonBateman&#44;MelissaMcCarthy&#44;JohnCho', 'USA', 'English', '2013-02-09', '01:51', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/q9MgSS0QvapgerVJ2C0Y6F8jOwx.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi618833689/', '25fa41563fa9446'),
(397, '2015-08-12 11:46:00', NULL, 1, 317, 'Side Effects', 'side_effects', 1, 'Emily Taylor&#44; despite being reunited with her husband from prison&#44; becomes severely depressed with emotional episodes and suicide attempts. Her psychiatrist&#44; Jonathan Banks&#44; after conferring with her previous doctor&#44; eventually prescribes an experimental new medication called Ablixa. The plot thickens when the side effects of the drug lead to Emily killing her husband in a &quot;sleepwalking&quot; state. With Emily plea-bargained into mental hospital confinement and Dr. Banks&#39; practice crumbling around him&#44; the case seems closed. However&#44; Dr. Banks cannot accept full responsibility and investigates to clear his name. What follows is a dark quest that threatens to tear what&#39;s left of his life apart even as he discovers the diabolical truth of this tragedy.                ', '<p>Emily Taylor&#44; despite being reunited with her husband from prison&#44; becomes severely depressed with emotional episodes and suicide attempts. Her psychiatrist&#44; Jonathan Banks&#44; after conferring with her previous doctor&#44; eventually prescribes an experimental new medication called Ablixa. The plot thickens when the side effects of the drug lead to Emily killing her husband in a &quot;sleepwalking&quot; state. With Emily plea-bargained into mental hospital confinement and Dr. Banks&#39; practice crumbling around him&#44; the case seems closed. However&#44; Dr. Banks cannot accept full responsibility and investigates to clear his name. What follows is a dark quest that threatens to tear what&#39;s left of his life apart even as he discovers the diabolical truth of this tragedy.                </p>\n', '58dfa4601f87337de42ee7b18dfeb559', 1, 1439372760, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '2053463', '109421', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ttD69Yhh2BV1WVqr27NRbF8ubOW.jpg', 'Crime&#44; Drama&#44; Thriller', 'Steven Soderbergh', 'RooneyMara&#44;ChanningTatum&#44;Ju