(437, '2015-08-12 11:48:00', NULL, 1, 357, 'The Last Waltz', 'the_last_waltz', 1, 'Thanksgiving&#44; 1976&#44; San Francisco&#39;s Winterland: the Band performs its last concert after 16 years on the road. Some numbers they do alone&#44; some songs include guest artists from Ronnie Hawkins (their first boss&#44; when they were the Hawks) to Bob Dylan (their last&#44; when as his backup and as a solo group&#44; they came into their own). Scorsese&#39;s camera explores the interactions onstage in the making of music. Offstage&#44; he interviews the Band&#39;s five members&#44; focusing on the nature of life on the road. The friendships&#44; the harmonies&#44; the hijinks&#44; and the wear and tear add up to a last waltz.                ', '<p>Thanksgiving&#44; 1976&#44; San Francisco&#39;s Winterland: the Band performs its last concert after 16 years on the road. Some numbers they do alone&#44; some songs include guest artists from Ronnie Hawkins (their first boss&#44; when they were the Hawks) to Bob Dylan (their last&#44; when as his backup and as a solo group&#44; they came into their own). Scorsese&#39;s camera explores the interactions onstage in the making of music. Offstage&#44; he interviews the Band&#39;s five members&#44; focusing on the nature of life on the road. The friendships&#44; the harmonies&#44; the hijinks&#44; and the wear and tear add up to a last waltz.                </p>\n', '6778e1fe943fde586cc4f4b886e6ce96', 1, 1439372880, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0077838', '13963', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mgn1rY1dAKsP4rJ75dX1OzEcW5K.jpg', 'Documentary&#44; Music', 'Martin Scorsese', 'RobbieRobertson&#44;MuddyWaters&#44;NeilYoung', 'USA', 'English', '1978-12-31', '01:57', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/yq2fgGCXO6Lf2nXrbIUZEUXQ99d.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi698680601/', 'da6c0d284bf7b01');
