(453, '2015-08-12 11:49:00', NULL, 1, 373, 'PK', 'pk', 1, 'P. K. is a comedy of ideas about a stranger in the city&#44; who asks questions that no one has asked before. They are innocent&#44; child-like questions&#44; but they bring about catastrophic answers. People who are set in their ways for generations&#44; are forced to reappraise their world when they see it from PK&#39;s innocent eyes. In the process PK makes loyal friends and powerful foes. Mends broken lives and angers the establishment. P. K.&#39;s childlike curiosity transforms into a spiritual odyssey for him and millions of others. The film is an ambitious and uniquely original exploration of complex philosophies. It is also a simple and humane tale of love&#44; laughter and letting-go. Finally&#44; it is a moving saga about a friendship between strangers from worlds apart.                ', '<p>P. K. is a comedy of ideas about a stranger in the city&#44; who asks questions that no one has asked before. They are innocent&#44; child-like questions&#44; but they bring about catastrophic answers. People who are set in their ways for generations&#44; are forced to reappraise their world when they see it from PK&#39;s innocent eyes. In the process PK makes loyal friends and powerful foes. Mends broken lives and angers the establishment. P. K.&#39;s childlike curiosity transforms into a spiritual odyssey for him and millions of others. The film is an ambitious and uniquely original exploration of complex philosophies. It is also a simple and humane tale of love&#44; laughter and letting-go. Finally&#44; it is a moving saga about a friendship between strangers from worlds apart.                </p>\n', '0fd9b7a136b71c3680082d24c370e3b9', 1, 1439372940, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '2338151', '297222', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dWUqNMxL2fMu1PlnRFLKvURi4rk.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Drama&#44; Romance&#44; Sci-Fi', 'Rajkumar Hirani', 'AamirKhan&#44;AnushkaSharma&#44;SanjayDutt', 'India', 'Hindi', '2