(464, '2015-08-12 11:49:00', NULL, 1, 384, 'Eastern Boys', 'eastern_boys', 1, 'They come from all over Eastern Europe: Russia&#44; Romania&#44; Ukraine. They are Eastern boys. The oldest appear no more than 25; as for the youngest&#44; there is no way of telling their age. They hang around the Gare du Nord train station in Paris. They might be prostitutes&#44; but there is no way of knowing for certain. Muller&#44; a discreet man in his late fifties has his eye on one of them - Marek. One afternoon&#44; Muller gathers his courage and speaks to him. The young man agrees to come visit Muller the following day&#44; at his place. However the next day&#44; when the doorbell rings&#44; Muller doesn&#39;t have the faintest idea that he has fallen into a trap.                ', '<p>They come from all over Eastern Europe: Russia&#44; Romania&#44; Ukraine. They are Eastern boys. The oldest appear no more than 25; as for the youngest&#44; there is no way of telling their age. They hang around the Gare du Nord train station in Paris. They might be prostitutes&#44; but there is no way of knowing for certain. Muller&#44; a discreet man in his late fifties has his eye on one of them - Marek. One afternoon&#44; Muller gathers his courage and speaks to him. The young man agrees to come visit Muller the following day&#44; at his place. However the next day&#44; when the doorbell rings&#44; Muller doesn&#39;t have the faintest idea that he has fallen into a trap.                </p>\n', '85a8d481ba56478dcf32c7525d39cdcd', 1, 1439372940, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '2991092', '214210', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5h1BJ7pLHqH9BYlpZzOx610kSYt.jpg', 'Drama', 'Robin Campillo', 'OlivierRabourdin&#44;KirillEmelyanov&#44;DaniilVorobyov', 'France', 'French', '2014-04-02', '02:08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3LXJGjS3zz5XhfgwUjlG2vc7Exl.jpg', NULL, 'a30b9e6bf0ae7f0'),
