(481, '2015-08-12 11:50:00', NULL, 1, 401, 'Blue Lagoon: The Awakening', 'blue_lagoon:_the_awakening', 1, 'In this passionate modern day retelling of the classic novel&#44; Emmaline Robinson and Dean McMullen are on two opposing sides of their high school world. But when they are caught in a storm at sea during a Caribbean field trip and stranded on a tropical island&#44; these two teenagers will have to come together in ways they never imagined. Without parents&#44; without cell phones and without help&#44; they will learn how to survive on their own or face the ultimate consequences. As they explore and learn about each other&#44; they also learn about themselves while falling in love&#44; while waiting for rescue on the island.                ', '<p>In this passionate modern day retelling of the classic novel&#44; Emmaline Robinson and Dean McMullen are on two opposing sides of their high school world. But when they are caught in a storm at sea during a Caribbean field trip and stranded on a tropical island&#44; these two teenagers will have to come together in ways they never imagined. Without parents&#44; without cell phones and without help&#44; they will learn how to survive on their own or face the ultimate consequences. As they explore and learn about each other&#44; they also learn about themselves while falling in love&#44; while waiting for rescue on the island.                </p>\n', '91fa1a598169f723eba2561ee4acc568', 1, 1439373000, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '2287663', '115290', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vg6SIzh3YbgvddmGE6vRbaDlsqD.jpg', 'Adventure&#44; Drama&#44; Romance', 'Mikael Salomon', 'IndianaEvans&#44;BrentonThwaites&#44;DeniseRichards', 'USA', 'English', '2012-06-16', '01:25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/qIO14kdtP547xUGXQyiE5HfjOWS.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi3586369561/', '9dad1efafd26136'),
