(517, '2015-08-12 11:51:00', NULL, 1, 437, 'The Constant Gardener', 'the_constant_gardener', 1, 'In a remote area of Northern Kenya&#44; activist Tessa Quayle is found brutally murdered. Tessa&#39;s companion&#44; a doctor&#44; appears to have fled the scene&#44; and the evidence points to a crime of passion. Members of the British High Commission in Nairobi assume that Tessa&#39;s widower&#44; their mild-mannered and unambitious colleague Justin Quayle&#44; will leave the matter to them. They could not be more wrong. Haunted by remorse and jarred by rumors of his late wife&#39;s infidelities&#44; Quayle surprises everyone by embarking on a personal odyssey that will take him across three continents. Using his privileged access to diplomatic secrets&#44; he will risk his own life&#44; stopping at nothing to uncover and expose the truth - a conspiracy more far-reaching and deadly than Quayle could ever have imagined.                ', '<p>In a remote area of Northern Kenya&#44; activist Tessa Quayle is found brutally murdered. Tessa&#39;s companion&#44; a doctor&#44; appears to have fled the scene&#44; and the evidence points to a crime of passion. Members of the British High Commission in Nairobi assume that Tessa&#39;s widower&#44; their mild-mannered and unambitious colleague Justin Quayle&#44; will leave the matter to them. They could not be more wrong. Haunted by remorse and jarred by rumors of his late wife&#39;s infidelities&#44; Quayle surprises everyone by embarking on a personal odyssey that will take him across three continents. Using his privileged access to diplomatic secrets&#44; he will risk his own life&#44; stopping at nothing to uncover and expose the truth - a conspiracy more far-reaching and deadly than Quayle could ever have imagined.                </p>\n', 'a8848b8504ad864b0a4527f84f109a59', 1, 1439373060, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0387131', '1985', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/r7QOXMcuIqZUeIVXVc4BCZrd9ni.jpg', 'Drama&#44; M