(529, '2015-08-12 11:51:00', NULL, 1, 449, 'Crossroads', 'crossroads', 1, 'Three best friends get together and bury a box&#44; making a pact to open it at midnight at their high school graduation. In the small town in Georgia that they live in&#44; things soon change. One is little miss perfect&#44; one is an engaged prom queen&#44; and the other is a pregnant outcast. On the night of their graduation&#44; they open the box and they strike up a conversation. Suddenly&#44; one brings up the topic of her going to Los Angeles for a record contract audition. They all decide to go together and they leave. With a little money&#44; they set out on the road with a guy named Ben. When one of them tells the other a rumor that he might be a homicidal maniac&#44; they are all scared of him. When they reach Los Angeles&#44; Lucy (Britney Spears) falls in love with Ben and against her father&#39;s wishes&#44; she stays and she goes to the audition.                ', '<p>Three best friends get together and bury a box&#44; making a pact to open it at midnight at their high school graduation. In the small town in Georgia that they live in&#44; things soon change. One is little miss perfect&#44; one is an engaged prom queen&#44; and the other is a pregnant outcast. On the night of their graduation&#44; they open the box and they strike up a conversation. Suddenly&#44; one brings up the topic of her going to Los Angeles for a record contract audition. They all decide to go together and they leave. With a little money&#44; they set out on the road with a guy named Ben. When one of them tells the other a rumor that he might be a homicidal maniac&#44; they are all scared of him. When they reach Los Angeles&#44; Lucy (Britney Spears) falls in love with Ben and against her father&#39;s wishes&#44; she stays and she goes to the audition.                </p>\n', '69509d04f66665fcf3819b447333f877', 1, 1439373060, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0275022', '17130', 'https://image.tmdb.org