(546, '2015-08-12 11:51:00', NULL, 1, 466, 'Braveheart', 'braveheart', 1, 'William Wallace is a Scottish rebel who leads an uprising against the cruel English ruler Edward the Longshanks&#44; who wishes to inherit the crown of Scotland for himself. When he was a young boy&#44; William Wallace&#39;s father and brother&#44; along with many others&#44; lost their lives trying to free Scotland. Once he loses another of his loved ones&#44; William Wallace begins his long quest to make Scotland free once and for all&#44; along with the assistance of Robert the Bruce.                ', '<p>William Wallace is a Scottish rebel who leads an uprising against the cruel English ruler Edward the Longshanks&#44; who wishes to inherit the crown of Scotland for himself. When he was a young boy&#44; William Wallace&#39;s father and brother&#44; along with many others&#44; lost their lives trying to free Scotland. Once he loses another of his loved ones&#44; William Wallace begins his long quest to make Scotland free once and for all&#44; along with the assistance of Robert the Bruce.                </p>\n', '7766c0398c7b91c3cb3a1aa7a740375e', 1, 1439373060, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0112573', '197', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2qAgGeYdLjelOEqjW9FYvPHpplC.jpg', 'Biography&#44; Drama&#44; History&#44; War', 'Mel Gibson', 'MelGibson&#44;SophieMarceau&#44;PatrickMcGoohan', 'USA', 'English', '1995-05-24', '02:58', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mXJnEzFHmchkMkuvaJ25eV4qWL5.jpg', NULL, 'f5fba7cd4163fd3');
