(570, '2015-08-12 11:52:00', NULL, 1, 490, 'Gone with the Wind', 'gone_with_the_wind', 1, 'Scarlett is a woman who can deal with a nation at war&#44; Atlanta burning&#44; the Union Army carrying off everything from her beloved Tara&#44; the carpetbaggers who arrive after the war. Scarlett is beautiful. She has vitality. But Ashley&#44; the man she has wanted for so long&#44; is going to marry his placid cousin&#44; Melanie. Mammy warns Scarlett to behave herself at the party at Twelve Oaks. There is a new man there that day&#44; the day the Civil War begins. Rhett Butler. Scarlett does not know he is in the room when she pleads with Ashley to choose her instead of Melanie.                ', '<p>Scarlett is a woman who can deal with a nation at war&#44; Atlanta burning&#44; the Union Army carrying off everything from her beloved Tara&#44; the carpetbaggers who arrive after the war. Scarlett is beautiful. She has vitality. But Ashley&#44; the man she has wanted for so long&#44; is going to marry his placid cousin&#44; Melanie. Mammy warns Scarlett to behave herself at the party at Twelve Oaks. There is a new man there that day&#44; the day the Civil War begins. Rhett Butler. Scarlett does not know he is in the room when she pleads with Ashley to choose her instead of Melanie.                </p>\n', '9ecf053a9a4c7529ca33c73f4bbfe431', 1, 1439373120, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0031381', '770', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2m9qsuDpAb6aBMxbKOBU1jsP9qf.jpg', 'Drama&#44; Romance&#44; War', 'Victor Fleming', 'ClarkGable&#44;VivienLeigh&#44;ThomasMitchell', 'USA', 'English', '1939-12-15', '03:58', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/bGRUMgSvs6wzYQRqehY4Fsup4f1.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi581873433/', '81a0dd2d614140f'),
