(578, '2015-08-12 11:53:00', NULL, 1, 498, 'Turbo', 'turbo', 1, 'From the makers of MADAGASCAR and KUNG FU PANDA&#44; TURBO is a high-velocity 3D comedy about a snail who dares to dream big - and fast. After a freak accident infuses him with the power of super-speed&#44; Turbo kicks into overdrive and embarks on an extraordinary journey to achieve the seemingly impossible: competing in the world&#39;s fastest race&#44; the Indianapolis 500. With the help of his tricked-out streetwise snail crew&#44; this ultimate underdog puts his heart and shell on the line to prove that no dream is too big&#44; and no dreamer too small.                ', '<p>From the makers of MADAGASCAR and KUNG FU PANDA&#44; TURBO is a high-velocity 3D comedy about a snail who dares to dream big - and fast. After a freak accident infuses him with the power of super-speed&#44; Turbo kicks into overdrive and embarks on an extraordinary journey to achieve the seemingly impossible: competing in the world&#39;s fastest race&#44; the Indianapolis 500. With the help of his tricked-out streetwise snail crew&#44; this ultimate underdog puts his heart and shell on the line to prove that no dream is too big&#44; and no dreamer too small.                </p>\n', '242943fb30823b1a54442be541b81e50', 1, 1439373180, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '1860353', '77950', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kajPlPUgobxci8ME5oqvzjN430q.jpg', 'Animation&#44; Adventure&#44; Comedy&#44; Family&#44; Sport', 'David Soren', 'RyanReynolds&#44;PaulGiamatti&#44;MayaRudolph', 'USA', 'English', '2013-07-19', '01:36', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dvdKrICCKP8Uh1Xqkn60oQXnYer.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi127903257/', '91833e9dcd0cfc6'),
