(586, '2015-08-12 11:53:00', NULL, 1, 506, 'The Chronicles of Narnia: Prince Caspian', 'the_chronicles_of_narnia:_prince_caspian', 1, 'The four Pevensie children return to Narnia&#44; only to discover that hundreds of years have passed since they ruled there&#44; and the evil King Miraz has taken charge. With the help of a heroic mouse called Reepicheep&#44; and the exiled heir to the throne&#44; Prince Caspian&#44; they set out to overthrow the King&#44; once again with Aslan&#39;s help.                ', '<p>The four Pevensie children return to Narnia&#44; only to discover that hundreds of years have passed since they ruled there&#44; and the evil King Miraz has taken charge. With the help of a heroic mouse called Reepicheep&#44; and the exiled heir to the throne&#44; Prince Caspian&#44; they set out to overthrow the King&#44; once again with Aslan&#39;s help.                </p>\n', '5f4ba71ce7450d6910f7959704953c97', 1, 1439373180, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0499448', '2454', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kSSyzqw9C4wUggicG4D81XmptR1.jpg', 'Action&#44; Adventure&#44; Family&#44; Fantasy', 'Andrew Adamson', 'BenBarnes&#44;SkandarKeynes&#44;GeorgieHenley', 'USA&#44; Poland&#44; Slovenia&#44; Czech Republic', 'English', '2008-05-16', '02:30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/eiET76GO3xECOic1rL8VcTLuy3L.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi1793261849/', '25abe539da37d50'),
(587, '2015-08-12 11:53:00', NULL, 1, 507, 'Horton Hears a Who!', 'horton_hears_a_who!', 1, 'One day&#44; Horton the elephant hears a cry from help coming from a speck of dust. Even though he can&#39;t see anyone on the speck&#44; he decides to help it. As it turns out&#44; the speck of dust is home to the Whos&#44; who live in their city of Whoville. Horton agrees to help protect the Whos and their home&#44; but this gives him nothing but torment from his neighbors&#44; who refuse to believe that anything could survive on the speck. Still&#44; Horton stands by the motto that&#44; &quot;After all&#44; a person is a person&#44; no matter how small.&quot;                ', '<p>One day&#44; Horton the elephant hears a cry from help coming from a speck of dust. Even though he can&#39;t see anyone on the speck&#44; he decides to help it. As it turns out&#44; the speck of dust is home to the Whos&#44; who live in their city of Whoville. Horton agrees to help protect the Whos and their home&#44; but this gives him nothing but torment from his neighbors&#44; who refuse to believe that anything could survive on the speck. Still&#44; Horton stands by the motto that&#44; &quot;After all&#44; a person is a person&#44; no matter how small.&quot;                </p>\n', '648049284615287a1d14bcfec120a29d', 1, 1439373180, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0451079', '12222', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/cYc2MbsXsDbMcf3tZDSiuNLn7kn.jpg', 'Animation&#44; Adventure&#44; Comedy&#44; Family&#44; Fantasy', 'Jimmy Hayward', 'JimCarrey&#44;SteveCarell&#44;CarolBurnett', 'USA', 'English', '2008-03-03', '01:26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jft2L1Jhe9xhKhB5uYBzYIjGXkw.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi1823605017/', 'a414d44d8b68bcc'),
