(595, '2015-08-12 11:53:00', NULL, 1, 515, 'Shiloh', 'shiloh', 1, 'An abused beagle runs away from his owner. On the road&#44; he meets young Marty Preston and follows him home. The boy immediately forms a bond with the dog and names him Shiloh. His stern father won&#39;t let him keep the dog because it belongs to Judd Travers&#44; a local hunter. After Shiloh is mistreated again&#44; he runs away and returns to Marty. Knowing his father will once again make him bring Shiloh back to Judd&#44; he makes a home for the dog in an old shed up the hill from the Prestons&#39; house and hides him from his family. His secret is soon discovered when a stray attacks the dog one night and he must turn to his father for help.                ', '<p>An abused beagle runs away from his owner. On the road&#44; he meets young Marty Preston and follows him home. The boy immediately forms a bond with the dog and names him Shiloh. His stern father won&#39;t let him keep the dog because it belongs to Judd Travers&#44; a local hunter. After Shiloh is mistreated again&#44; he runs away and returns to Marty. Knowing his father will once again make him bring Shiloh back to Judd&#44; he makes a home for the dog in an old shed up the hill from the Prestons&#39; house and hides him from his family. His secret is soon discovered when a stray attacks the dog one night and he must turn to his father for help.                </p>\n', 'd41a953f7569982611dcc589b58b03ba', 1, 1439373180, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0120118', '33660', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jnhjXhqjH4MnGFGQOlYigZhVH6O.jpg', 'Drama&#44; Family', 'Dale Rosenbloom', 'BlakeHeron&#44;MichaelMoriarty&#44;ScottWilson', 'USA', 'English', '1996-11-30', '01:33', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2zrN90JBPZ2WGgrCasw0OeQeLj4.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/imdb/vi493289497/', '8e4a06d1adccc2d'),
