(631, '2015-08-12 11:55:00', NULL, 1, 551, 'Matilda', 'matilda', 1, 'A grouchy couple are parents to a very sweet girl&#44; Matilda. Unlike her bratty brother and mean parents&#44; Matilda becomes a very sweet and extremely intelligent 6 year old girl&#44; who is very keen to go to school and read books. After a while&#44; her parents send her to school with the worst principal in the world&#44; a very sweet teacher&#44; and good friends. While trying to put up with her parents&#39; and principal&#39;s cruelty&#44; she starts to unwittingly unleash telekinetic powers&#44; destroying a television and making a newt fly onto the principal. With enough practice&#44; Matilda starts to learn to control her telekinetic powers and soon using them on her principal so she can drive her away from the school.                ', '<p>A grouchy couple are parents to a very sweet girl&#44; Matilda. Unlike her bratty brother and mean parents&#44; Matilda becomes a very sweet and extremely intelligent 6 year old girl&#44; who is very keen to go to school and read books. After a while&#44; her parents send her to school with the worst principal in the world&#44; a very sweet teacher&#44; and good friends. While trying to put up with her parents&#39; and principal&#39;s cruelty&#44; she starts to unwittingly unleash telekinetic powers&#44; destroying a television and making a newt fly onto the principal. With enough practice&#44; Matilda starts to learn to control her telekinetic powers and soon using them on her principal so she can drive her away from the school.                </p>\n', '3978c72394df04d0801c4fdb0d1589a0', 1, 1439373300, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0117008', '10830', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vddUwPL3L8MBH4FrEDCAZM9T6sj.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Fantasy', 'Danny DeVito', 'DannyDeVito&#44;RheaPerlman&#44;MaraWilson', 'USA', 'English', '1996-07-28', '01:38', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/r8nIuvtJBmFvvW07KmOGKKm6NQF.jpg', 'http://www.imdb.com/video/im