(634, '2015-08-12 11:55:00', NULL, 1, 554, 'Death Becomes Her', 'death_becomes_her', 1, 'Helen&#44; a writer&#44; and Madeline&#44; an actress&#44; have hated each other for years. Madeline is married to Ernest&#44; who was once Helen&#39;s fiance. After she recovers from a mental breakdown&#44; Helen vows revenge by stealing back Ernest and plotting to kill Madeline. Both rivals have secretly drunk a miracle cure for aging; they accidentally discover&#44; when each tries to eliminate the other&#44; that they have become immortal and that &quot;life&quot; will never be the same again.                ', '<p>Helen&#44; a writer&#44; and Madeline&#44; an actress&#44; have hated each other for years. Madeline is married to Ernest&#44; who was once Helen&#39;s fiance. After she recovers from a mental breakdown&#44; Helen vows revenge by stealing back Ernest and plotting to kill Madeline. Both rivals have secretly drunk a miracle cure for aging; they accidentally discover&#44; when each tries to eliminate the other&#44; that they have become immortal and that &quot;life&quot; will never be the same again.                </p>\n', '936caeff65634d57c1ae1aa1c73e8f44', 1, 1439373300, 0, 'always', 'live', 'markdown', '', '0104070', '9374', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/qNIkecw9i44ljTJaMfkdeyLc4vB.jpg', 'Comedy&#44; Fantasy', 'Robert Zemeckis', 'MerylStreep&#44;BruceWillis&#44;GoldieHawn', 'USA', 'English', '1992-07-30', '01:44', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rbh1X7khOI8nv9nprC1OVwXl9ZJ.jpg', NULL, '78a5350f0bee5bf'),
